      h1 Group 5. Economic opportunities and policy responses
    .description
      p This chapter explores Uzbekistan’s investments in the transition to a green economy and the economic opportunities and benefits green growth generates. The indicators help assess policy effectiveness in green technology and innovation, environment investment and financing, prices, environmental taxes (revenues) and financial transfers. In this way, they capture the economic opportunities associated with green growth (OECD, 2017).
