          i.fa-solid.fa-file-circle-check
          h3 Policy responses indicators: Key findings
        #section-2
          i.fa-solid.fa-seedling
          h3 5.1 Technology and innovations
        #section-3
          i.fa-solid.fa-hand-holding-hand
